Package: rSky
Title: An R package for interacting with Bluesky.social
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("D.", "Scarnecchia", , "scarnecchia@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of rSky is to provide R users with some basic tools for authenticating to and fetching data from Bluesky. It currently has limited functionality.
